    narr:generatedFrom "f8129fac4673b1c046ab8d5cb019704466b73550" ;
    narr:narration """This hub tracks the [authoritative register](narr:StyleObs_Tone_Authoritative) defining aswritten’s internal documentation. The style is characterized by [active, agent-first voice](narr:StyleObs_ActiveVoice) and [short, punchy declarative sentences](narr:StyleObs_ShortPunchyCadence) that function as design mantras. Conviction is signaled through [emphatic ALL-CAPS](narr:StyleObs_AllCapsEmphasis), including a recurring [ALL-CAPS 'IS'](narr:StyleObs_AllCapsIS) for identity claims, and [bold markdown](narr:StyleObs_BoldConviction) reserved for irreversible architectural decisions. The register is highly self-aware, employing [epistemic precision](narr:Style_EpistemicPrecision) to distinguish between 'leaning' and 'decision,' and using [block-quoted corrections](narr:StyleObs_BlockquoteCorrections) to retract prior conflations. This tone extends beyond the founder to [customer CTOs](narr:StyleObs_CustomerCTOGuardPullRequests_Imperative) and collaborators, framing the product as [its own first user](narr:StyleObs_FirstUserPositioning). The narrative trajectory moves from [early imperative workflow lists](narr:StyleObs_BulletedDecisionLists) toward a more [refined, sectioned analytical voice](narr:StyleObs_SectionedNarrativeVoice) that treats [epistemological terms](narr:StyleObs_EpistemologicalRegister) as precise technical constraints rather than metaphors.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_10> ;
